snippet.title: The Bathrooms | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
👀 WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2778080/The_Bathrooms/?utm_source=youtube

Navigate the cold, endless halls of The Bathrooms in search of your lost dog and use tools to survive. But beware, The Custodian is aware of your presence and is learning about you. Your escape from this nightmare depends on your wit and skill.

Trailer music by the talented @AvithOrtega. 🎧👀
